    },
    {
      "text": "\n                  \n                    Theodore Schleifer\n                                        \u2022\n                    June 21, 2022\n                  \n\n                  Thiel vs. Hoffman: Stanford Takes Toledo\n\n                  \n                    \n                      \n                        \n                      \n                    \n                    \n                      As young undergraduates at Stanford in the late 1980s, Peter Thiel and Reid Hoffman bonded over dorm-room political debates, relishing the back-and-forth so much that they ran for student office together on a joint ticket that promised to tackle the university\u2019s bureaucracy, from the right and the left, respectively. When they left The Farm, the [\u2026]\n                      READ FULL STORY\n                    \n                  \n                ",
      "url": "https://puck.news/thiel-vs-hoffman-stanford-takes-toledo/"
    },
    {
      "text": "MORE SILICON VALLEY STORIES",
