      "text": "\n            Baratunde Thurston\n            A best-selling author, podcast and television host, and cultural critic focused on the intersection of race, tech, democracy, and climate change in America.\n          ",
      "url": "https://puck.news/author/baratunde-thurston/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n            Dylan Byers\n            A veteran media reporter who has served at NBC News, CNN, and Politico, reporting on the business of media, technology, and entertainment.\n          ",
      "url": "https://puck.news/author/dylan-byers/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n            Eriq Gardner\n            Former legal editor-at-large at The Hollywood Reporter; now Founding Partner and National Correspondent for Puck, reporting on the intersection of law, media, Hollywood, and Wall Street.\n          ",
      "url": "https://puck.news/author/eriq-gardner/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n            Julia Ioffe\n            A veteran of The Atlantic, The New Yorker, and Politico reporting from Washington, D.C. on politics and media after Trump.\n          ",
      "url": "https://puck.news/author/julia-ioffe/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n            Matthew Belloni\n            Formerly the editor of The Hollywood Reporter, and an entertainment lawyer, Belloni covers the inside conversation about money and power in Hollywood.\n          ",
      "url": "https://puck.news/author/matthew-belloni/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n            Peter Hamby\n            Emmy award-winning journalist and host of Snapchat\u2019s Good Luck America, reporting on politics, media, and technology.\n          ",
      "url": "https://puck.news/author/peter-hamby/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n            Tara Palmeri\n            A former Playbook lead author and ABC News White House Correspondent, now reporting on the convergence of Capitol Hill, K Street, the West Wing, and the D.C. media companies who cover it all.\n          ",
      "url": "https://puck.news/author/tara-palmeri/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n            Theodore Schleifer\n            A former Recode and CNN reporter, now covering power, influence, and money in Silicon Valley.\n          ",
      "url": "https://puck.news/author/theodore-schleifer/"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n            Tina Nguyen\n            Formerly a political correspondent at Politico and Vanity Fair, chronicling the egos and intrigues inside Trumpworld.\n          ",
